      <abstract>
        <p>Advertising account changes noted (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Sizzler International, Culver City, Calif., to Glass McClure Advertising, Sacramento, Calif., to handle the account of the restaurant chain, which had been at Evans, Hardy &amp; Young, Santa Barbara, Calif. Billings were estimated at $10 million.</p>
      </block>
